N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 8 ยง 309.10 - Liability for payments

State Regulations

The benefits payable under the plan shall be made by the
insurer pursuant to contract, and neither the State nor the State University
shall be liable for such benefits. Notes
